Purchase officer for an Aluminum Company
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/05 10:14:20
Ref. JB3047418
Job Description
The candidate will be reporting to the Purchase manager. The candidate's job description has as follows:
- send inquiries to suppliers to procure the right material, services and equipment at the right time;
- endeavor to obtain as full and open competition as possible on all purchases;
- keep and maintain the data entry on our ERP system for all our purchases ;
- Confirm with the suppliers the ETA of goods and services and inform the stores;
-
Keep informed of current developments in the field of purchasing, prices, market conditions and new products;
- Supervise the inspection of all supplies, services and equipment purchased to insure conformance with specifications;
- Maintain a bidders’ list, vendors’ file, and such other records as are needed for the efficient operation of the purchasing function;
Skills
Microsoft outlook , Focus ERP system , Excellent English
Education
Higher Education
